Diagram 1 (Hasty)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is a hasty attack.
\par
\par When black plays dansu at 2, white has no way to continue the attack. White has allowed black's group to live.
\par
\par
\par }
